"{\"uid\": \"straitstimes.com-sport-french-gloom-clouds-paris-olympics-six-months-from-start\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Choose edition  Search  singapore  asia  world  opinion  life  business  sport  Visual  Podcasts  SPH Rewards  STClassifieds  Paid press releases  Advertise with us  FAQs  Contact us  Sign up now:Get the biggest sports news in your inbox  Paris 2024 organisers remain confident that sights such as beach volleyball in front of the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2271622778635843e-21, \"text\": \"SPH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\"}, {\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"score\": 0.9604822703099307, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Advertise\", \"types\": [\"Q7377\", \"Q729\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\"}, {\"begin\": 239, \"end\": 249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.511176669049053e-31, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: AFP  PublishedJan 22, 2024, 05:46 PM  UpdatedNov 08, 2024, 01:37 PM  PARIS-Political bickering, ongoing grumbling about ticket prices and disruption to everyday life are souring the mood in the build-up to the Paris Olympics in July - something organisers blame on typical French pessimism.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 643, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 626, \"end\": 632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9989523057643498, \"rank\": 0.0009813069967032695, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several recent announcements have led to a spike in negative publicity for the sporting mega-event which will start in just six months and draw a television audience of billions.\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 823, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Many Parisians were dismayed in December by news that transport ticket prices are set to double for the duration of the event and that they should work from home to free up seats on busy metros and buses.\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 1029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The unveiling of planned security measures led to claims some parts of the city would face Covid-19-style lockdowns, while controversy erupted about the environmental impact of a judges' tower at the surfing venue in French Polynesia.\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1255, \"end\": 1264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9848748267072021, \"rank\": 0.015357454636188768, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On top of it all, Paris' Socialist Mayor Anne Hidalgo and President Emmanuel Macron's centrist government fell out publicly after Hidalgo claimed that planned Paris transport upgrades would \\\"not be ready\\\".\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1472, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1285, \"end\": 1290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8320413056720383e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1308, \"end\": 1320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}, {\"begin\": 1335, \"end\": 1350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1397, \"end\": 1404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"score\": 0.9999999729852792, \"rank\": 2.7014931806700076e-08, \"text\": \"Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\"}, {\"begin\": 1426, \"end\": 1431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8320413056720383e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There have been a succession of issues that have been badly handled from a communication point of view,\\\" said Philippe Moreau Chevrolet, a lecturer in communication at Sciences Po university in Paris and the founder of the MCBG Conseil public relations agency.\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1594, \"end\": 1600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gustave_Moreau\", \"score\": 0.4506317107272318, \"rank\": 0.6199794082868836, \"text\": \"Moreau\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gustave_Moreau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gustave_Moreau\"}, {\"begin\": 1601, \"end\": 1610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chevrolet\", \"score\": 0.9992740088363085, \"rank\": 0.0007255310576381044, \"text\": \"Chevrolet\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chevrolet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chevrolet\"}, {\"begin\": 1643, \"end\": 1665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sciences_Po\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sciences Po university\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sciences_Po\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sciences_Po\"}, {\"begin\": 1669, \"end\": 1674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8320413056720383e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Instead of getting people behind the Games, they have created mistrust.\\\"\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"France's association of hoteliers and restaurant owners issued an unusual statement earlier in January, condemning French politicians for their \\\"anxiety-inducing\\\" announcements around the Games and urging them to come together.\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 2039, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1812, \"end\": 1818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9579291103760884, \"rank\": 0.03791431880673877, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1927, \"end\": 1933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9989523057643498, \"rank\": 0.0009813069967032695, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In general, we would strongly urge all of our public authorities, collectively and with solidarity, to speak positively and responsibly,\\\" the statement added.\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2200, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Other recent complaints centre on the construction work that snares traffic daily around the capital, while resentment lingers over the handling of ticket sales in 2023 that saw many locals priced out.\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2403, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris will see \\\"the most expensive ticket prices in an athletics arena that we have witnessed at an Olympic Games\\\", said World Athletics president Sebastian Coe in December, adding he was worried the families of some athletes would be unable to attend.\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2657, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2405, \"end\": 2410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8320413056720383e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2526, \"end\": 2541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5837963048664949e-13, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}, {\"begin\": 2552, \"end\": 2565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sebastian Coe\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 organisers remain confident that sights such as beach volleyball in front of the Eiffel Tower, swimming in the River Seine, or the marathon through the capital's fabled streets will lift spirits once the flame is lit on July 26.\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2781, \"end\": 2792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They make a distinction between the often noisy and attention-seeking media and political debate, and wider public opinion.\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 3023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A survey by the Odoxa group for RTL radio in November suggested that 65 per cent of French people were in favour of the Games - a fall of 11 points in two years but still a large majority with positive views.\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3233, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3109, \"end\": 3122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the Paris region, slightly more than half of people were in favour.\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3242, \"end\": 3247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8320413056720383e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers also point to the orderly preparations, as well as their budget restraint in comparison with other modern editions.\", \"from\": 3307, \"to\": 3433, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of the sporting infrastructure is finished.\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3483, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes' village is almost ready to be furnished.\", \"from\": 3484, \"to\": 3538, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Crucial metro and train line extensions will be ready in time, they insist.\", \"from\": 3539, \"to\": 3614, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What if everything went OK?\\\"\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3645, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"asked a headline in the left-wing Liberation newspaper at the start of 2024.\", \"from\": 3646, \"to\": 3722, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"France is ready for the Olympics... but given the country's gloomy mood and its unpopular leaders, there is no sign of popular fervour,\\\" it added.\", \"from\": 3724, \"to\": 3871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3725, \"end\": 3731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9579291103760884, \"rank\": 0.03791431880673877, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tony Estanguet, the head of the Paris 2024 organising committee, has criticised \\\"Olympics bashing\\\" in the media and despaired of his compatriots' tendency to look on the downside.\", \"from\": 3873, \"to\": 4052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3873, \"end\": 3887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}, {\"begin\": 3905, \"end\": 3915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.511176669049053e-31, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We like to look at what is not going well, focus on things that are out of place, concentrate on our weak spots, whereas some countries like to play up their qualities and strengths,\\\" he told France Inter radio in January.AFP  Olympics 2024  Olympics  France  E-paper  Newsletters  Podcasts  RSS Feed  About Us  Terms & Conditions  Personal Data Protection Notice  Need help?\", \"from\": 4054, \"to\": 4430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4247, \"end\": 4259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_Inter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"France Inter\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_Inter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_Inter\"}, {\"begin\": 4307, \"end\": 4313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9579291103760884, \"rank\": 0.03791431880673877, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 4347, \"end\": 4355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RSS Feed\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reach us here.\", \"from\": 4431, \"to\": 4445, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertise with us\", \"from\": 4447, \"to\": 4464, \"entities\": []}]}"